hadiths[129]{hadithnumber,text}:
2753,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein jihad key liye nikalta hai Allah ney uskey liye (ye ajr aur sawab) tayyar kiya hai (ke wo farmata hai : ) ye shakhs sirf meri raah mein jihad key liye , mujh par eman rakhtey huye aur merey Rasulon ko sachcha maan kar nikla hai, usliye main isey zamanat deta hun ke ya usey (shahadat sey sarfaraaz kar key) jannat mein dakhil kar dunga, ya usey hasil honey waley sawab ya ghanimat key sath , usey uskey ghar mein wapis pahuncha dunga jis sey wo nikla tha. phir farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar ye baat na hoti ke meri wajeh sey musalmanon ko mashaqqat (aur takleef) hogi , main kabhi Allah ki raah mein nikalney waley kisi jihaadi dastey sey peechhey na rehta , lekin merey paas itni gunjaaish nahin hoti ke unhen sawariyan mohaiyya kar sakoon. aur unkey paas itni taqat nahin hoti ke (apney kharch par) merey sath (jihad key liye) chaley jaaeyn, aur na mujh sey peechhey rehney par unkey dil mutmain hotey hain (isliye main bhi baaz oqaat jihad key liye janey waley lashkar key sath nahin jata). qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! mujhey to ye chiz mehbub hai ke main Allah ki raah mein jang kar key shaheed ho jaun , phir jang karun aur shaheed ho jaun , phir jang karun aur shaheed ho jaun."
2754,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ko Allah ki taraf sey ye zamanat hasil hai ke wo usey ya to (shahadat ki maut dey kar) apni bakhshish aur rehmat key daman mein ley leyga, ya phir sawab aur ghanimat key sath wapis (ghar) ley aayega. Allah ki raah mein jihad karney wala , wapsi tak us roza rakhney waley aur qiyam karney waley ki tarah (sawab hasil karta) hai jo (nafli rozon aur nafli namazon sey) thakta nahin."
2755,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki raah mein (guzarney wali) eik subah ya eik Sham duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us sey behtar hai."
2756,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki raah main eik subah ya eik Sham duniya sey aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us sab sey behtar hai."
2757,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki raah main eik subah ya eik Sham yaqinan duniya sey aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us sab sey behtar hai."
2758,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jisney Allah ki raah mein jang karney waley ko itna saman diya ke usey (jihad key silsiley mein) kisi chiz ki (mazeed) zarurat na rahi, us ko itna sawab milega jitna us Mujahid ko shahadat ya wapsi tak milega."
2759,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Allah ki raah mein jang karney waley ko saman mohaiyya kiya, usey bhi us (Mujahid) key barabar sawab milega jabke Mujahid key sawab mein koi kami nahin hogi."
2760,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka kharch kiya huwa sab sey afzal Dinar wo hai jo wo ehal-o-ayaal (biwi bachhon) par kharch karta hai, aur wo Dinar jo wo Allah ki raah (jihad) mein ghodey par kharch karta hai, aur wo Dinar jo aadmi Allah ki raah mein (jihad key doran mein) apney sathiyon par kharch karta hai."
2761,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib, Hazrat Abu-Darda , Hazrat Abu-Hurera , Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli, Hazrat Abdullah bin umr , Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr , Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah aur Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein kharch bhejta hai aur khud ghar mein muqeem rehta hai, usey eik dirham key badley mein saat sau dirham ka sawab milta hai. aur jo shakhs khud Allah ki raah mein jang karta hai aur is silsiley mein kuchh kharch karta hai, usey eik dirham key badley mein saat lakh dirham ka sawab milta hai. iskey baad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat ki(وَاللهُ يُضَاعِفُ لِمَنْ يَّشَاءُ),''aur Allah Taala jis key liye chahta hai sawab dugna kar deta hai.''"
2762,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney na jihad kiya, na kisi Mujahid ko samaan mohaiyya kiya, aur na kisi Mujahid ki ghair haziri mein uskey ghar walon ki achchhi tarah khabar geeri ki to Allah Taala usey qiyamat sey pehley hi kisi aafat mein mubtala kar dega."
2763,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah sey is haal mein milta hai ke uska Allah ki raah (jihad) mein koi hissa nahin to wo Allah sey aeb-daar ho kar milta hai."
2764,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwaae-tabuk sey wapsi par Madina Munawra key qarib pahunchey to farmaya : Madina mein kuchh afrad hain ke tum ney jo bhi safar kiya, aur jo bhi wadi tey ki, wo is main tumharey sath they. Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aur wo Madina mein hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (haan) wo Madina mein hain. unhen kisi uzr ney rok liya tha."
2765,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madina mein kuchh afrad hain, tum ney jo wadi tey ki aur jis raastey par chaley (un sab mein) wo tumharey sath sawab mein shareek rahey (kyonkey) unhen uzr ney (jihad mein janey sey) rok diya tha. Imam abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : ya jis tarah Shaikh (Ahmed bin Sanan) ney kaha : mainey is hadees ko wesey hi lafz balafz likha hai."
2766,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon sey khitab kartey huye farmaya : aey logo ! mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey eik hadees suni thi jo tum sey sirf isliye bayan nahin ki thi ke main tumhen apney sath rakhney ki shadeed khahish rakhta tha. ab (ye hadees sun kar) har shakhs ko ikhtiyar hai, chahey apni zaat key liye (is azeem amal ka) intikhaab karey , ya na kerey. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki raah main eik raat mahaaz par rehta hai to usey eik hazar raat key qiyam aur rozon ka sawab milta hai."
2767,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein mahaaze-jang par jihad key liye tayyar honey ki haalat mein faut huwa to wo jo nek amal karta tha, Allah uskey liye us amal ka sawab jari farma deta hai. aur uska rizq jari farma deta hai usey aazmaney walon (Munkir, Nakeer) ka khof nahin hota. aur Allah usey qiyamat key din khof sey mehfooz uthaeyga."
2768,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan key siwa kisi aur mahiney mein musalmanon ki sarhad par khatrey ki jagah eik din sawab ki niyat sey Allah ki raah mein theherna sau saal ki ibadat, yani itney arsey key rozon aur tahajjud sey ziyada sawab ka baais hai. aur Ramzan key mahiney mein musalmanon ki sarhad par khatrey ki jagah Allah ki raah main eik din sawab ki niyat sey theherna eik hazar saal ki ibadat, yani itney arsey key rozon aur tahajjud sey ziyada sawab ka baais hai. agar Allah Taala us (nek amal key karne waale) ko sahih salaamat uskey ghar ley aaya to hazar saal tak uskey gunah nahin likhey jaeyngey aur nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur usey qiyamat tak sarhad ki rakhwali ka sawab milta rahega."
2769,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala muhaafizon (musalmanon ka difaa karney waley mujahideen) ka pehra deney waley par rehmat farmaaey."
2770,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : Allah ki raah main eik raat pehra dena ghar main eik hazar saal tak rozey rakhney aur qiyam karney sey afzal hai jabke har saal teen sau saath din ka ho aur har din hazar saal key barabar ho."
2771,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : main tujhey Allah sey darney ki aur har buland jagah takbir kehney ki wasiyat karta hun."
2772,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr huwa to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab logon sey ziyada Haseen, sab sey ziyada sakhi aur sab sey ziyada bahaadur they. eik raat Madiney walon ko (dushman key hamley ka) khatra mehsus huwa, chunanche wo log aawaz ki taraf gaey to (raastey mein) unhen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) miley. aap un sey pehley aawaz ki taraf tashrif ley gaey they (aur halaat ka jayeza ley kar wapis tashrif la rahey they). aap Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key eik ghodey ki nangi peeth par sawar they jis par kaathi nahin thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key galey mein talwaar (latak rahi) thi aur aap farma rahey they : logo ! mat ghabraaon. aap unhen wapis janey ko keh rahey they, phir ghodey key barey mein farmaya : hamney isey samandar (ki tarah subuk raftaar) paya. ya farmaya : ye to samandar hai. (hadees key Raavi) Hammad bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Sabit (Rahimahullah) ney ya (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key) kisi aur shagrid ney farmaya : ye Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik ghoda tha jo bahut sust raftaar tha. us din key baad kabhi koi ghoda us sey aagey nahin guzar saka."
2773,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tumhen (jihad key liye) nikalney ko kaha jaey to nikla karo."
2774,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman key andar Allah ki raah mein udney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan (dono) jama nahin ho saktey."
2775,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo eik baar Allah ki raah mein nikla , usey jitna gardo-ghubar pahunchega , qiyamat key din usey itni kastoori milegi."
2776,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni khaala Hazrat Umme Haram binte Milhaan (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat ki unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas (merey ghar mein) so gaey phir muskuraatey huye bedaar huye to mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap kyon hans rahey hain? aap ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuchh afrad mujhey dikhaye gaey, jo samandar ki pusht par is tarah sawar they (aur kashtiyon mein is shaan sey bethey they) jaisey badshah apney takhton par hotey hain. Umme Haram (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : Allah sey dua farmaiye ke mujhey un mein shamil farma dey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey liye dua farmaai. phir aap dobara so gaey, phir aisey hi huwa. Umme Haram (Raziallahu anha) ney wohi baat arz ki aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi pehley wala jawab diya. unhoney (dobara) kaha : Allah sey dua kijiye ke mujhey un mein shamil kar dey. to aap ney farmaya : to pehley giroh mein sey hai. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya : jab musalmanon ney Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath pehla samandari safar kiya to Umme Haram (Raziallahu anha) bhi apney shohar Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) key sath jihad key liye rawana huin. jab wo log jang sey wapis aaye to (safar key doran mein) Sham mein (eik maqam par) thehrey. (rawangi key waqt) sawar honey key liye sawari ka janwer aap key qarib laya gaya to us (janwer) ney unhen gira diya aur wo faut ho gaeen."
2777,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : samandar main eik jang karna khushki mein das jangein ladney key barabar hai. aur jis shakhs ka (samandari safar ki wajeh sey) samandar mein sar chakraata hai, wo Allah pak ki raah mein apney khoon sey aalooda ho kar tadapne waley ki tarah hai."
2778,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : samandar ka shaheed khushki key do shaheedon key barabar hai. aur samandar (key safar) mein jis ka sar chakraata hai, wo khushki mein apney khoon sey aalooda ho kar tadapne waley ki tarah hai. aur do mojon key darmiyan (ka fasla tey karney wala) aisa hai jaisey Allah ki raah mein sari duniya ka fasla tey karney wala. Allah Taala ney maut key farishtey ko roohen qabz karney par muqarrar kiya hai siwaye samandar key shaheed key, un ki roohen Allah Taala khud qabz karta hai. wo khushki key shaheed key sarey gunah bakhsh deta hai siwaye qarz key, aur samandar key shaheed key gunah bhi bakhsh deta hai aur qarz bhi."
2779,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar duniya ka sirf eik din bhi baqi reh jaey, tab bhi Allah Taala us din ko lamba kar dega yahan tak key merey ghar walon (ehale-bait) mein sey eik aadmi (Mehdi) badshah baneyga. wo dailam key pahad aur Qustuntuniya key shehar par qabza kerega."
2780,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey liye ilaqey Fateh hongey. tum eik shehar Fateh karogey jis ka naam qazween hoga. jo shakhs us ko Fateh karney key liye chaalis din ya chaalis raat mahaaz par mojud raha, usey jannat mein soney ka eik sutoon milega, is par eik sabz (hara) zumurrud hoga jis par surkh yaqut ka eik khema hoga. uskey sattar hazar darwazey hongey jo soney key hongey. har darwazey par khoobsurat aakhon wali hooron mein sey us (jannati) ki eik biwi mojud hogi."
2781,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Jaahma Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap key sath mil kar jihad karna chahta hun, us sey mera maqsad Allah ki raza aur aakhirat key ghar (jannat) ka husool hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tera bhala ho, kya teri maa zinda hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. farmaya : wapis ja kar uski khidmat kar. phir mainey dusri taraf sey aa kar arz kiya. aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap key sath mil kar jihad karna chahta hun, us sey mera maqsad Allah ki raza aur aakhirat key ghar (jannat) ka husool hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tera bhala ho, kya teri maa zinda hai? mainey kaha : ji haan Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : wapis ja kar uski khidmat kar. phir main Rasoolullah key samney sey aaya aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main aap key sath mil kar jihad karna chahta hun, us sey mera maqsad Allah ki raza aur aakhirat key ghar (jannat) ka husool hai. aap ney farmaya : tera bhala ho, kya teri maa zinda hai? mainey kaha : ji haan, aey Allah key Rasool ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tera bhala ho, uskey qadmon mein pada reh, jannat wahin hai. Harun bin Abdullah Hammal key wastey sey marvi riwayat mein hai ke Hazrat Jaahma (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar (oopar darj baat) arz ki thi. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Jaahma (Raziallahu anhu) unhi Abbas bin Mirdas Sulmi (Raziallahu anhu) key betey hain jinhoney ghazwaae Hunain key moqey par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey shikwa kiya tha."
2782,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main Allah ki raza aur aakhirat key ghar key husool ki gharz sey aap key sath jihad ki niyat sey hazir huwa hun. jab main aaya to merey maa baap ro rahey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wapis ja kar unhen isi tarah hasaao (khush karo) jis tarah unhen rulaayaa (aur ghamgin kiya) hai.
2783,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya ke eik aadmi bahaaduri key izhar key liye jang karta hai, eik aadmi apney qabiley ki himayat mein ladtaa hai, eik aadmi dikhlaao key liye ladtaa hai. (kya unhen bhi Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley shumar kiya ja sakta hai)? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is maqsad key liye jang karta hai ke Allah ka kalma (Islam) buland ho, wo Allah ki raah mein (jihad karney wala) hai."
2784,"Hazrat Abu-Uqba (Rasheed Faarsi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ye kisi Faarsi key azad karda ghulam they. unhoney farmaya : jang-uhad key moqey par main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath (jihad mein) hazir tha. mainey eik mushrik mard par zarab lagai aur kaha : ye lo, main Faarsi jawan hun. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko malum hui to aap ney to farmaya : tu ney ye kyon na kaha : ye lo, main Ansari jawan hun."
2785,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo jamaat Allah ki raah mein jang karti hai aur un afrad ko ghanimat hasil ho jati hai to wo apna do tihai sawab jaldi (duniya hi mein) wasul kar letey hain. agar unhen ghanimat na miley to (aakhirat mein) purey sawab key mustahiq hotey hain."
2786,"Hazrat Urwa Baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon sey qiyamat tak khair baandh di gaee hai."
2787,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak khair hai."
2788,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak key liye khair hai. ya farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon sey qiyamat tak khair baandh di gaee hai. (phir farmaya : ) ghodey teen tarah key hain : wo kisi key liye sawab ka baais hotey hain, kisi key liye (izzat qaaim rakhney wala) parda hotey hain aur kisi key liye (gunah ka) bojh hotey hain. ye sawab ka baais us shakhs key liye hain jo Allah unhen ki raah mein (jihad key liye) rakhta aur tayyar karta hai. ye ghodey apney peton mein jo kuchh daltey hain (uskey iwaz) Malik key liye sawab likha jata hai. agar wo unhen kisi charaagaah mein charaaey to ye jo kuchh khaeyngey, uskey badley mein us (Malik) key liye sawab likha jaaeyga. agar wo unhen behti nehar (ya darya) sey pani pilaaeyga to wo jo qatra apney peton mein dalengey, uskey badley mein us (Malik) ko sawab milega--------. Raavi ney ghodon key peshab aur leed par sawab milney ka bhi zikr kiya hai . . . . . . . . agar wo (rassi aur lagaam sey azad ho kar apni marzi sey) eik do chakkar lagaeyn to unkey har qadam key badley mein (Malik key liye) sawab likha jaeyga. aur ye pardey ka baais us shakhs key liye hain jo unhen izzat aur zeenat key liye paaltaa hai, aur tangi turshi ho ya aasani, wo un ki peethon aur peton ka haq faraamosh nahin karta. aur ye gunah ka baais us shakhs key liye hain jo unhen fakhr, ghuroor, takabbur aur logon ko dikhaney key liye rakhta hai. to ye is par (gunah ka) bojh hain."
2789,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Haris bin Rabaee) Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen ghoda wo hai jo siyah ho, peshani par thoda sa safed nishan ho, chaaron paaon mein safedi ho, naak aur ooper wala hont safed ho, aglaa daayan paon safed na ho. agar siyah (mushki) rang na ho to inhi sifaat ka hamil (rakhne-wala) kamiyat ghoda umda hai."
2790,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wo ghoda pasand na tha jis key teen paon safed hon aur eik safed na ho.
2791,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jisney Allah ki raah mein (jihad key liye) ghoda baandh rakha, phir apney haath sey uska chaara tayyar kiya to usey har daney key badley main eik neki milegi."
2792,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : jo musalman mard Allah ki raah mein itni der ladaai kerey. jitna oontni ka doodh dobaara dohney key darmiyan waqfa hota hai, uskey liye jannat wajib hai."
2793,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik jang mein shareek huwa. (us jang mein) Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye rajz (veer ras / bahaduri paida karne wala kalaam) kahi : aey meri jaan ! to jannat ko kyon na pasand karti hai? main Allah ki qism kha kar kehta hun tujhey zarur us (key husool key liye maidan jang) mein khushi sey utarna hoga, warna tujhey is par majbur kya jaeyga."
2794,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa jihad afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : jis ka khoon baha diya gaya aur uska ghoda bhi qatl ho gaya (uska jihad behtareen hai)."
2795,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein zakhmi hota hai, aur ye baat Allah hi janta hai ke kon uski raah mein zakhmi hota hai, wo qiyamat key din is andaz sey hazir hoga ke uska zakham aisa hi (taza) hoga jaisey zakhmi honey key din tha. uska rang khoon ka hoga aur mehak kastoori ki hogi."
2796,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (dushmanon ki) jamaaton key khilaf dua farmaai. aur farmaya : ( اللَّهُمَّ مُنْزِلَ الْكِتَابِ سَرِيعَ الْحِسَابِ اهْزِمْ الْأَحْزَابَ اللَّهُمَّ اهْزِمْهُمْ وَزَلْزِلْهُمْ ), ''aey Allah ! aey kitab nazil karney waley ! aey jald hisab leney waley ! jamaaton ko shikast dey dey. aey Allah ! unhen shikast dey aur unhen ladkhadaa dey."
2797,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala sey sachhey dil sey shahadat ki dua karta hai to Allah Taala usey shaheedon key darjaat tak pahuncha deta hai, chahey wo apney bistar hi par faut ho."
2798,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney shaheedon ka zikr huwa to aap ney farmaya : zamin sey shaheed ka khoon khushk bhi nahin huwa hota ke uski dono biwiyan (hooren) itni tezi sey uskey paas aati hain jaisey doodh pilaney wali do daaiyaan jo be-aab-we-giyaah zamin (marusthal) mein apney bachhey gum kar bethi hon (to wo un ki talash mein be qarar ho kar bhaagti phirti hain). dono hooron key haath main eik joda hota hai jo duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai us sey behtar hota hai.
2799,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key paas shaheed key liye chhe inaamat hain : khoon key pehley qatrey key sath hi uski maghfirat ho jati hai, usey jannat mein uska thikana dikha diya jata hai, usey azabe-qabr sey mehfooz rakha jata hai, wo (qiyamat key din) badi ghabrahat sey mehfooz rahega, usey eman ka libase-faakhraa (qimti libaas) pehnaya jaeyga, khoobsurat aakhon wali hooron sey uski shaadi kar di jaeygi aur uskey sattar rishtey daaron key haq mein uski shafaat qubul ki jaeygi."
2800,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke jange-uhud key din jab ( Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) key walid) Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Haram (Raziallahu anhu) qatl (shaheed) kar diye gaey to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jabir ! kya main tujh ko bataun ke Allah ney terey walid sey kya farmaya? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala har kisi sey pas parda reh kar kalam farmata hai lekin terey walid sey aamney samney kalam farmaya. Allah ney un sey farmaya : merey bandey ! koi khahish kar main tujhey dunga. unhoney (Hazrat Abdullah bin Haram (Raziallahu anhu) ney) arz kiya : aey merey Malik ! mujhey zinda kar dey taake main dobara teri raah mein shaheed ho jaun. Allah ney farmaya : mera ye faisla pehley jari ho chuka hai ke faut honey waley dobara duniya mein nahin bhejey jaeyngey. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ya Rab ! merey pasmandagaan ko mera pegham pahuncha dey. to Allah ney ye sari aayat nazil farmaai : (وَلا تَحسَبَنَّ الَّذينَ قُتِلوا فى سَبيلِ اللَّهِ أَموتًا), ""jo log Allah ki raah mein qatl (shaheed) kar diye jaeyn unhen murda na samjho."" (Sura Aale-Imran : 169)"
2801,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney is aayat mubaraka key barey mein farmaya ( وَلا تَحسَبَنَّ الَّذينَ قُتِلوا فى سَبيلِ اللَّهِ أَموتًابَل اَحيَاءٌ عِندَرَبِّهِم يُرزَقُونَ ),""jo log Allah ki raah mein qatl (shaheed) kar diye jaeyn unhen murda na samjho, balke wo apney Rab key paas zinda hain, unhen rizq diya jata hai."" (Sura Aale-Imran : 169)unhoney farmaya : hamney is aayat mubaraka key barey mein daryaft kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shaheedon ki roohen sabz (hare) parindon ki tarah jannat mein jahan chahti hain charti chugti phirti hain, phir arsh sey latki hui qindeelon mein baseraa karti hain. usi haal main eik din Allah Taala ney un ki taraf dekh kar farmaya : mujh sey jo chaho mang lo. unhoney kaha : ya Rab ! hum tujh sey kya maangen? hum to jannat mein jahan chahtey hain khatey peetey ghoomtey hain. jab unhoney dekha ke unhen us waqt tak nahin chhoda jaeyga jab tak kuchh sawal na karen to unhoney kaha : (aey Allah ! ) hum tujh sey ye sawal kartey hain ke hamari roohen hamarey jismon mein dal kar hamein dobara duniya mein bhej dey taake phir teri raah mein shaheed ho jaeyn. jab Allah ney dekha ke unka aur koi mutalba nahin to unhen chhod diya gaya."
2802,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shaheed ko qatl hotey waqt sirf itni takleef hoti hai jitni kisi ko chewnti key kaatney sey hoti hai."
2803,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo bimar huye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un ki iyaadat key liye tashrif ley gaey. ghar walon mein sey kisi ney kaha : hamein to ummid thi ke wo Allah ki raah mein qatl ho kar shahadat ki maut paeyngey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (agar sirf maidane-jang mein marna hi shahadat hai) tab to meri ummat key shaheed bahut thodey hongey. Allah ki raah mein qatl hona shahadat hai. taaoon sey marna bhi shahadat hai. aur jo aurat hamal key haalat mein faut ho jaey wo bhi shaheed hai. doob kar marney wala, jal kar marney wala aur zaatul-janb ki bimari sey marney wala bhi shaheed hai."
2804,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum log shaheed key barey mein kya kehtey ho (ke shaheed kon hota hai)? haazirin ney kaha : Allah ki raah mein qatl ho jana (shahadat hai). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab to meri ummat key shaheed thodey hi hongey. jo Allah ki raah mein qatl ho gaya, wo shaheed hai. aur jo Allah ki raah mein faut ho gaya, wo bhi shaheed hai. aur pet ki bimari sey marney wala shaheed hai. taaoon sey marney wala shaheed hai.  eik riwayat mein hai : aur doob kar mar janey wala shaheed hai."
2805,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka key din Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap key sar par khud tha.
2806,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-uhud key din do zirhen ooper nichey pahnin."
2807,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Habib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. unhoney hamari talwaaron ko kuchh chaandi sey muzayyan dekha to naraz huye aur farmaya : logon ( Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum) ko badi badi futoohaat hasil huin, un ki talwaarein to soney chaandi sey muzayyan nahin thin lekin (un par) seesa, loha aur ilaabi (laga hota tha). Abul-Hasan Qataan ney farmaya : ilaabi patthey ko kehtey hain."
2808,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni talwaar ""Zulfaqaar"" jange-badar key moqey par ghanimat mein sey li thi."
2809,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath jihad key liye tashrif ley jatey to apney sath neza bhi utha kar ley jatey. jab wapis hotey to neza wahin phenk detey, is khayal sey ke koi utha kar ley aayega. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataunga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) sey) farmaya : aisa na karo, agar tum aisa karogey to haqiqat mein gumshuda chiz bhi koi nahin uthaaeyga."
2810,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath mein Arbi kamaan thi. aap ney eik shakhs key haath mein Faarsi kamaan dekhi to farmaya : ye kya hai? isey phenk do. tum is tarah ki (Arbi) kamaanein aur neze istimal kiya karo, Allah Taala in key zariey sey Deen mein tumhari madad farmaeyga, aur tumhen mulkon mein iqtidar ata farmaeyga."
2811,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala eik teer ki wajeh sey teen aadmiyon ko jannat mein dakhil farma deta hai. eik usey bananey wala jabke wo usey bananey mein neki ka sawab hasil honey ki ummid rakhta ho, aur (doosra) usey chalaney wala , aur (teesra) usey (teer andaz ko) pakdaaney wala. aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teer chalaao aur sawari karo. aur tumhara teer andazi karna mujhey tumhari ghud-sawari sey ziyada pasand hai. musalman tafrih key tor par jo kaam bhi karta hai wo batil (be kaar) hai, siwaye kamaan sey teer chalaney aur ghodon ko tarbiyat deney key aur biwi sey dil lagi karney key, isliye ke ye (teeno kaam) haq hain."
2812,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs dushman ki taraf eik teer phenkey aur wo dushman tak pahunch jaey, chahey dushman ko lagey ya na lagey, wo eik ghulam azad karney key barabar hai."
2813,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye aayat tilawat kartey suna : (وَأَعِدّوا لَهُم ما استَطَعتُم مِن قُوَّةٍ), ""dushman key muqabley key liye jitni ho sakey, taqat tayyar rakho. phir teen baar farmaya : khabrdar ! taqat sey murad teer andazi hai."""
2814,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jisney teer andazi seekhi, phir chhod di, usney meri nafarmani ki."
2815,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuchh afrad key paas sey guzrey jo teer andazi kar rahey they. aap ney farmaya : Ismail key beto ! teer chalaao , tumharey baap-daada bhi teer andaz they."
2816,"Hazrat Haris bin Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Madiney aaya to mainey dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey hain aur Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) galey mein talwaar latkaaey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney khadey hain. mujhey eik siyah jhandaa nazar aaya. mainey kaha : ye kon hai? logon ney bataya : ye Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) hain, jihad sey aaye hain."
2817,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka key din Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ka jhandaa safed tha.
2818,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bada jhandaa siyah aur chhota jhandaa safed tha.
2819,"Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney resham key batanon wala eik jubba nikala aur farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye libas us waqt pehantey they jab (jang mein) dushman key muqabil hotey."
2820,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo bareek resham aur motey resham sey mana farmatey they magar jo itna sa ho, usey jayez farmatey they. ye kehtey huye Raavi (Abu-Usman (Rahimahullah)) ney eik ungli sey ishara kiya, phir dusri ungli sey, phir teesri ungli sey, phir chauthi ungli sey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein is sey mana farmatey they."
2821,"Hazrat Amr bin Hures (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (wo manzar ab bhi merey tasawwur mein hai) goya main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke aap ney siyah amama pehan rakha hai aur uskey dono kinarey (past ki taraf) dono kandhon key darmiyan latak rahey hain."
2822,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huye to aap ney siyah amama pehan rakha tha.
2823,"Hazrat Khaarija bin Zaid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik aadmi ko dekha ke merey walid (Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey poochh raha tha ke agar eik aadmi jihad karey aur ghazwey key doran mein kharid aur farokht aur tijarat bhi karey to kya hukm hai? merey walid ney farmaya : hum tabuk mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hum kharid aur farokht kartey they, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen dekhtey they aur mana nahin farmatey they."
2824,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ye baat duniya aur jo kuchh usme hai sey ziyada mehbub hai ke eik subah ya eik Sham Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ko alwidaa karun aur uskey saman ki dekh bhaal karun."
2825,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey rukhsat kartey waqt farmaya : (أَسْتَوْدِعُكَ اللَّهَ الَّذِي لَا تَضِيعُ وَدَائِعُهُ), ''mein tujhey Allah key supurd karta hun jis key supurd ki hui cheezen zaya nahin hotin."""
2826,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab lashkar rawana farmatey they to rawana honey waley sey farmatey : (أَسْتَوْدِعُ اللَّهَ دِينَكَ وَأَمَانَتَكَ وَخَوَاتِيمَ عَمَلِكَ), ''main tera deen, teri amanat aur terey kaam key anjam ko Allah ki hifazat mein deta hun.''"
2827,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Iksim bin June Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Iksim ! apney qabiley key siwa dusron key sath mil kar jihad kar, tera akhlaq behtar ho jaeyga, aur terey sathiyon ki nazar mein teri izzat hogi. Iksim ! behtareen sathi chaar hain, behtareen dasta chaar sau ka hai, aur behtareen lashkar chaar hazar ka hai, aur baara hazar (ki fauj) ko tadaad kam honey ki wajeh sey shikast nahin ho sakti."
2828,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log baaten kiya kartey they ke jange Badr mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sathi teen sau das sey kuchh ziyada they, jitni tadaad Talut key sath nehar paar karney walon ki thi. unkey sath sirf eman rakhney waley nehar sey paar pahunchey they."
2829,"Hazrat Abu-Vard (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : aisa lashkar mat bano jo jang ka moqey aaye to (maidan chhod kar) bhag jaey aur agar usey ghanimat miley to khayanat karey."
2830,"Hazrat Halab Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey esaiyon ka khana khaney key barey mein daryaft kiya to aap ney farmaya : terey dil mein koi khana khatkaa paida na karey jis sey nasraniyat sey teri mushaabihat ho jaey."
2831,"Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum mushrikon ki handiyon mein khana pakka liya keren? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un mein khana na pakaao. mainey kaha : agar hamein zarurat pesh aa jaey aur in ko istimal kiye baghair chaara na ho to kya keren? aap ney farmaya : unhen achchhi tarah dho lo, phir (un mein khana) pakka kar kha lo."
2832,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum mushrik sey madad nahin letey. (Imam Ibne-Maja key ustad) Ali bin Muhammad ney apni hadees mein Raavi key barey mein taraddud (sankoch) ka izhar kiya hai ke wo Abdullah bin Yazeed hai ya Abdullah bin Zaid hai."
2833,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jang dhoka hai."
2834,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jang dhoka hai (ya jang dhoka deney wali hai)."
2835,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko qism kha kar ye farmatey suna : ye aayat (هَذَانِ خَصْمَانِ اخْتَصَمُوا فِي رَبِّهِمْ فَالَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا قُطِّعَتْ لَهُمْ ثِيَابٌ مِنْ نَارٍ) sey (عَذَابَ الْحَرِيقِ), ""ye dono mukhalif apney Rab key barey mein ikhtilaf karney waley hain. . . Allah Taala jo chahta hai karta hai.'' ghazwae-badar key din chhe afrad key barey mein nazil hui. Hazrat Hamza bin Abdul-Muttalib, Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib aur Hazrat Ubeda bin Haris Raziallahu anhum (eik taraf) Utba bin Rabeea, Sheeba bin Rabeea aur Waleed bin Utba (doosri taraf) jange-badar key din ye log (haq aur batil key) dalaeyl (ko taslim karney ya na kerney) ki wajeh sey eik doosrey key muqabil they."
2836,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik aadmi ka muqabla kiya aur usey qatl kar diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska saman mujhey dlwaya."
2837,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein eik maqtool (kafir) ka zaati saman dlwaya jisey unhoney jange-Hunain mein qatl kiya tha.
2838,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (jang mein kisi kafir ko) qatl karey to us (maqtool) ka zaati saman us (qatil) ka hai."
2839,"Hazrat Sa'ab bin Jassaasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya ke agar mushrekin ki kisi basti par shabb khoon (chhaapa) maara jaey aur us doran mein aurton aur bachchon ko nuqsan pahunchey (wo zakhmi ya qatl ho jaeyn to kya hukm hai)? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo bhi unhi mein sey hain."
2840,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein hamney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki qiyaadat mein qabila banu Hawazin sey jang ki. hum banu-Fazara key eik chashmey par pahunchey aur raat ke aakhiri hissey wahan tahrey rahey. jab subah hui to hamney un par hulla bol diya. hamney chashmey walon par shab-khoon (chhaapa) maar kar unhein qatl kar diya. wo nau ya saat ghar they."
2841,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raastey main eik maqtool aurat dekhi to aurton aur bachchon ko qatl karney sey mana farma diya.
2842,"Hazrat Hanzala Kaatib (Hanzala bin Rabee Tameemi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik ghazwey mein gaey. hamara guzar eik maqtool aurat (ki laash) key paas sey huwa. uskey paas log ikhattey ho gaey they. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye jagah bana di. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aurat to jang karney walon key sath jang mein shareek honey wali na thi. phir eik aadmi sey farmaya : Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jao aur usey kaho : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aap ko hukm detey hain ke bachchon ko aur mazduron ko hergiz qatl na keren. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey ye riwayat isi tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai. Abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba ney kaha : Sufiyan Sory ney is hadees mein ghalati ki hai ke unhoney isey Hanzala sey riwayat kiya hai."
2843,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Ubni naami basti ki taraf bheja to farmaya : subah key waqt Ubni jao aur usey nazar aatish kar (aag laga) do."
2844,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (yahudiyon key qabiley) banu Nazeer key khajuron key darakhton ko jala diya aur kaat diya. ye maqam (jahan khajuron key ye baagh waqey they) buwera kahlaataa hai. tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : (ما قَطَعْتُم مِّن لِّينَةٍ أَوْ تَرَكْتُمُوهَا قَائِمَةً - - - - - - -),''tum ney khajuron key jo darkht kaat daley ya jinhen tum ney un ki jadon par baqi rehney diya (ye sab Allah key farman sey tha aur isliye bhi ke Allah faasiqo ko ruswa karey)."""
2845,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney banu-Nazeer key khajuron key darkht jalaey aur kaatey aur usi key barey mein shayer ney kaha : (فَهَانَ عَلَى سَرَاةِ بَنِي لُؤَيٍّ حَرِيقٌ بِالْبُوَيْرَةِ مُسْتَطِيرُ), ''Banu-Luee (Quraish) key sardaron key liye aasan ho gaya ke buwera mein har taraf phailti hui aag lagi ho.''"
2846,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki qiyaadat mein qabila Hawazin sey jang ki (aur Fateh pai). unhoney mujhey banu-Fazara ki eik ladki inaam key tor par ata farmaai jo Arab ki intahaai Haseen aurton mein sey thi. usney purani posteen odh rakhi thi. mainey Madina pahunch janey tak uska kapda bhi (uskey jism sey) hata kar na dekha. (Madiney mein) mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bazar mein miley to farmaya : tera bhala ho, ye mujhey hiba kar do. mainey wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hiba kar di. aap ney isey (Makkey) bhej kar uskey badley mein un musalman qaidiyon ko chuda liya jo makkey mein qaid they."
2847,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mera eik ghoda bhag gaya to usey dushman ney pakad liya, phir (jang key baad) is par musalmanon ney qabza kiya to wo wapis mujhey (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ko) dey diya gaya. ye waqia Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney ka hai. (uskey ilawa) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ka eik ghulam bhag gaya aur Romiyon sey ja mila. musalmanon ney un par Fateh pai to Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ney wo ghulam dobara Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ko dey diya. ye waqiaa Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad ka hai."
2848,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Ashja' ka eik aadmi khabeer mein (jang key doran mein) faut ho gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney sathi ka janaza padh lo. logon ko is par tajjub huwa aur chehron par herat key aasaar zahir huye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye dekha to farmaya : tumharey sathi ney Allah ki raah mein (jihad key doran mein, ghanimat mein) khayanat ki hai. Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Sahaba ney uskey saman ki talashi li to yahudiyon key chand mankey miley jinki qeemat do dirham key barabar bhi nahin thi."
2849,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key saman ki dekh bhaal par eik aadmi mutayyan tha jisey Karkarah kehtey they. wo faut ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo jahannam mein hai. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum dekhney lagey (ke iski kya wajeh ho sakti hai) to unhein uskey paas eik chadar ya abaa mili jo usney (maale-ghanimat mein sey) churaa li thi."
2850,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ghazwae-Hunain key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein ghanimat key eik oont key paas khadey ho kar namaz padhaai, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney oont key thodey sey baal liye, unhein apni do ungliyon mein pakda aur farmaya : aey logon ye bhi tumhari ghaneematon mein sey hain. sooi-dhaaga aur us sey kam-o-besh chiz bhi ada karo. (ghaneemat mein) khayanat, qiyamat key din khayanat karney waley key liye aar (sharm), aeb aur aag bin jaeygi."
2851,Hazrat Habib bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khums key baad tihai hissa bator inaam diya.
2852,Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney shuru mein chotha hissa aur wapsi mein teesra hissa bator inaam ata farmaya.
2853,Hazrat Rajaa bin Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke hamein Amr bin Shuaib ney apney walid key wastey sey Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat bayan ki ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad koi zayed inaam nahin. qawi musalman zaeef musalmanon ko bhi (ghanimat mein sey) hissey den.Rajaa bin Abu-Salma farmatey hain : mainey suna ke Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Musa (Rahimahullah) unhein (Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) ko) keh rahey they : mujhey Makhool ney Habib bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) sey hadees sunai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney shuru mein chothai aur wapsi mein tihai inaam ata farmaya. Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : main tumhen apney walid ki apney daada sey riwayat suna raha hun aur tum mujhey Makhool ki riwayat suna rahey ho?
2854,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-khaibar key moqey par sawar ko teen hissey ata farmaaey, do hissey ghodey key aur eik hissa aadmi ka."
2855,"Hazrat Aabil-Laham (Raziallahu anhu) . . Wakee (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : (un ka ye naam isliye mashhoor huwa ke) wo gosht nahin khatey they. . . . key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Umer (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ghazwae-Khaibar key moqey par jabkey main ghulam tha, main apney aaqa key sath jihad mein shareek huwa to mujhey ghanimat mein sey (azad mardon ki tarah) hissa nahin mila. mujhey maamuli saman mein sey eik talwaar di gaee. jab main usey galey mein latkaataa to wo zamin par ghisat'ti thi."
2856,"Hazrat Umme Atiya Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath saat jangon mein hissa liya. (Sahaba key jang key liye chaley janey par) main khemon mein rehti (saman ki hifazat karti), unkey liye khana tayyar karti, zakhmiyon ka ilaj karti aur bimaron ki dekh bhaal karti."
2857,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein eik lashkar mein (eik jangi muhim par) rawana kiya to (alwidaa kehtey waqt) aap ney farmaya : Allah key naam sey , Allah ki raah mein chalo. Allah key sath kufr karney walon sey jang karo aur moosla na karna , ehad shikni na karna, maale-ghanimat mein khayanat na karna aur kisi bachchey ko qatl na karna."
2858,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi shakhs ko lashkar ka Ameer muqarrar farmatey to usey khud apni zaat key barey mein Allah sey darney ki nasihat kartey aur sath waley musalmanon key sath achchha sulook karney ki nasihat kartey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (mujahideen ko nasihat kartey huye) farmatey they : Allah key naam sey, Allah ki raah mein jihad karo. Allah key sath kufr karney walon sey jang karo. jihad karo aur (jihad key doran mein) ehad shikni na karna, khayanat na karna, moosla na karna aur kisi bachchey ko qatl na karna. (aur Ameere-lashkar ko nasihat farmatey : ) jab terey mushrik dushmanon sey tera samna ho to unhen teen baaton ki dawat dey. wo un mein sey jo baat bhi maan lein usey qubul kar key un sey haath rok ley (aur jang na kar). unhein (pehley) Islam ki dawat dey. agar wo ye baat maan lein (aur musalman ho jaeyn) to unka ye amal qubul kar ley (unhein musalman taslim kar ley) aur un sey haath rok ley, phir unhein dawat dey ke apney ilaqey (daarul kuffar) sey hijrat kar key muhajrin key ilaqey (daarul-Islaam) mein aa jaeyn. aur unhen bata ke agar wo hijrat kerengey to in ko muhajrin key huquq hasil hongey, aur un par muhajrin key faraaiz aaid hongey. agar wo (hijrat sey) inkar karen to unhein bata dena ke unhein Erabi (dehati) (khana-badosh) musalmanon waley huquq hasil hongey. un par Allah ka wo qanoon nafiz hoga jo (aam) momineen par nafiz hai. aur unhein maale-fai aur maale-ghanimat mein sey hissey nahin milenge, siwaye us surat key ke wo musalmanon key sath mil kar jang karen. (lekin) agar wo log Islam mein dakhil honey sey inkar kar den to un sey jiziya ki adaegi ka mutalba kar agar wo (ye mutalba) taslim kar lein to un sey (jiziya) manzoor kar key haath rok ley. agar wo (jiziya deney sey bhi) inkar karen to unkey khilaf Allah sey madad ki dua kar aur un sey jang kar. agar to kisi qiley ka muhaasra karey aur wo tujh sey mutalba karen ke to unkey liye Allah ka aur apney Nabi ka zimma dey (Allah aur uskey Rasool ki zimme-daari par aman dey) to unhein Allah ke zimme na dena aur apney Nabi ke zimme na dena, balke apna , apney baap ka aur apney sathiyon ka zimma dena kyonkey agar tum apna aur apney baapon ka wada tod dogey to wo Allah aur uskey Rasool ka zimma todney sey halka gunah hoga. agar to kisi qiley ka muhaasra karey aur wo Allah ka faisla qubul kartey huye (qiley sey) dast bardar honey par raza-mandi ka izhar karen to unhein Allah key faisley par dast bardar honey ko mat keh balke unhein apna faisla qubul karney (ka mutalba kartey huye usi shart) par dast bardar honey ka keh kyonkey tujhey nahin malum ke to Allah key faisley key mutabiq (faisla) kar sakeyga ya nahin. hadees key rawaa Hazrat Alqama bin Murtad kehtey hain : mainey ye hadees Muqaatil bin Hayyan ko bayan ki to unhoney kaha : mujhey Muslim bin Haizam ney Noman bin Muqrin key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah hadees bayan ki hai."
2859,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney meri itaat ki, usney Allah ki itaat ki. aur jisney meri nafarmani ki, usney Allah ki nafarmani ki. jisney Imam ki itaat ki, usney meri itaat ki. aur jisney Imam ki nafarmani ki, usney meri nafarmani ki."
2860,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno aur itaat karo agar-che tum par eik Habshi ghulam ko Haakim bana diya jaey jis ka sar munaqqey jaisa ho."
2861,"Hazrat Umme Husain (binte Is-haq) (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : agar tum par eik naak kaan kataa Habshi ghulam bhi Ameer muqarrar kiya jaey to uski baat suno aur taslim karo jab tak wo tumhein Allah ki kitab key mutabiq ley kar chaley."
2862,Hazrat Abdullah bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Rabzaa tashrif laye to namaz ki iqaamat ho chuki thi aur eik ghulam un ki imaamat kara raha tha. (usey) kaha gaya : ye Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) (aagey hain). wo peechhey hatney laga (taake Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) namaz padhaaen) to Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : merey khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey wasiyat ki hai ke main sunoon aur manun agar-che (Haakim) naak kaan kataa Habshi ghulam hi ho.
2863,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Alqama bin Mujazzir (Raziallahu anhu) ki qiyaadat main eik lashkar rawana farmaya. main bhi is mein shamil tha. jab wo (lashkar) ghazwey key maqam par pahuncha ya abhi raastey hi mein tha ke fauj key eik hissey ney (dushman par hamla karney mein pehal karney key liye aagey janey ki) ijazat talab ki. Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein ijazat dey di aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Huzaafa bin Qais Sahami (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka Ameer Muqarrar kiya. main un logon mein shamil tha jinhoney un (Abdullah bin Huzaafa (Raziallahu anhu)) key sath mil kar jang ki. abhi wo raastey hi mein they (dushman sey aamna samna nahin huwa tha) ke (us dastey key) logon ney sardi sey bachao key liye ya kisi aur maqsad key liye aag jalaai. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kuchh mazaahiya tabiyat rakhtey they. unhoney (sathiyon sey) kaha : kya mera hukm sun kar itaat karna tum par lazim nahin? unhoney kaha : lazim hai- farmaya : main tumhein jo bhi hukm dun kya tum mano gey? unhoney kaha : haan. farmaya : main tumhein qataee hukm deta hun ke is aag mein chhalaangen laga do. (ye hukm sun kar) baaz afrad uth khadey huye aur chhalaangen laganey ko tayyar ho gaey. jab Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney dekha ke ye log (aag mein) kudne waley hain to farmaya : ruk jao, main to tum sey mazaq kar raha tha. (Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) jab hum wapis (Madina) aaye to Sahaba ney ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key saamne rakhi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : in (Ameeron) mein sey jo koi tumhen Allah ki nafarmani ka hukm dey , uski itaat na karo."
2864,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman aadmi par (Ameer ki) itaat farz hai, chahey dil chahey ya na chahey, siwaye uskey ke kisi gunah ka hukm diya jaey. jab kisi gunah ka hukm diya jaey to na sun'na hai aur na man'na hai."
2865,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad kuchh aisey log bhi tumhare maamlat key nigraan (aur tumharey hukmran) hongey jo sunnat ki roshni ko bujhaaeynge, bidat par amal paira hongey , aur namaz ko (afzal) waqt sey der kar key padhengey. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool agar main unhein paaon to kya karun? aap ney farmaya : aey Umme Abd key betey ! mujh sey poochhtey ho ke kya karogey ? jo shakhs Allah ki nafarmani kerey. uski koi itaat nahin."
2866,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey baiat ki ke hum (har haal mein) sunengey aur taameel kerengey, mushkil mein bhi, aasani mein bhi, dil ki aamaadagi ki haalat mein bhi aur tabai nagawari ki haalat mein bhi, aur us waqt bhi jab hum par (doosron ko) tarjeeh di jaey. aur hukumat key maamlat mein hum ehale-hukoomat sey kash-ma-kash nahin kerengey. aur hum jahan bhi hongey sach kahengey. aur Allah (ki raza-mandi key kaam) mein kisi malamat karney waley ke malamat sey nahin darengey."
2867,"Hazrat Abu-Muslim (Abdullah bin Soob Kholani) (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai unhoney kaha : mujhey piyarey dayanatdar Sababi Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai. wo mujhey piyarey they aur meri nazar mein diyanat-daar they. unhoney farmaya : hum saat ya aath ya nau afrad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum Allah key Rasool ki baiat nahin karogey? hamney haath badha diye. eik sahab ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum aap ki baiat kar chukey hain. (ab) kis baat par baiat keren? aap ney farmaya : is baat par ke Allah ki ibadat karogey, uskey sath kisi chiz ko shareek nahin karogey, paanchon namazein qaaim karogey aur hukm sun kar manogey. phir aahista sey eik baat farmaai : aur logon sey kuchh nahin maangogey. Abu-Muslim (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mainey un mein sey eik sahab ko dekha ke (sawari par bethey huye) unka koda (haath sey chhoot kar) gir padta tha to kisi ko ye nahin kehtey they ke ye koda pakda den (khud sawari sey utar kar utha letey they)."
2868,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney sama' aur itaa'at (hukm ko tawajjoh sey sun kar puri tarah itaat kerney) par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum sey jis qadr mumkin ho."
2869,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik ghulam ney hazir ho kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey hijrat ki baiat kar li. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko malum na tha ke wo ghulam hai. (baad mein) uska aaqa usey leney aa gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye (ghulam) merey haath farokht kar do. chunanche aap ney do siyah faam (rang) ghulamon key iwaz usey kharid liya. uskey baad aap ye puchhey baghair kisi sey baiat nahin letey they ke kya wo ghulam hai?"
2870,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmi hain jin sey Allah Taala qiyamat key din kalam nahin kerega, na un ki taraf (nazare-rehmat sey) dekhega, na unhein paak kerega, aur unkey liye dard-naak azab hai. (eik) wo aadmi jo biyaabaan main apni zarurat sey zayed pani par (qaabiz) hai, musafir ko nahin leney deta. (doosra) wo aadmi jisney Asr key baad kisi aadmi ko koi chiz bechi, (bhaaw tey kartey waqt) Allah ki qism kha kar kaha ke usney ye chiz itney ki li thi, gaahak ney isey sachcha samajh liya, halanke wo sachcha na tha. (teesra) wo aadmi jisney kisi Imam (khalifa ya uskey naaib) ki baiat ki aur baiat sirf duniya key (husool key) liye ki. agar is (Imam) ney duniya ka kuchh maal dey diya to wo wafadar raha aur agar usey kuchh na diya to usney bhi wafaa na ki."
2871,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bani-Israel key (intizami, muaashrati, deeni aur duniyaawi) umoor ki dekh bhaal unkey anbiyaae-kiraam kartey they. jab koi Nabi faut ho jata to doosra Nabi uska janashin ho jata. (lekin) merey baad tumharey andar koi Nabi aaney wala nahin. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! phir (un maamlat ka) kya hoga? aap ney farmaya : khulafaa hongey, aur bahut ziyada hongey. unhoney arz kiya : phir hum kya keren? farmaya : pehley khalifa ki baiat par qaaim raho, phir uskey baad jo (baiat key lihaz sey) pehla ho. tum par jo faraaiz hain ada karo, unkey faraaiz key barey mein Allah Taala un sey poochh taachh farmaeyga."
2872,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har ehad shikan (waada todne wale) key liye qiyamat key din jhandaa nasab kiya (gaada) jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ye falan ki ehad shikni (todna) hai."
2873,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din har ehad shikan (waada todne wale) key liye uske waada todne key mutabiq jhandaa nasab kya (gaada) jaeyga."
2874,"Hazrat Umaima binte Raqeeqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main kuchh khawatin key sath baiat karney key liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein farmaya : jin kamon ki tumhein istataat aur taqat ho (un mein merey hukm ki taameel zaruri hai). main aurton sey musaafa nahin karta."
2875,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Zauja Mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : momin aurten jab hijrat kar key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hoti thin to aap Quran Majeed ki is aayat mubaraka key mutabiq un sey iqrar letey they : ( يَا أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ إِذَا جَاءَكَ الْمُؤْمِنَاتُ يُبَايِعْنَكَ ) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : jis momin aurat ney in chizon ka iqrar kar liya, usney aazmaaish (mein pura utarney) ka iqrar (aur waada) kar liya. jab aurten zaban sey bol kar unka iqrar kar leti thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhein farmatey : jao mainey tum sey baiat ley li. qism hai Allah ki ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath kabhi kisi (ajnabi) aurat key haath sey mas nahin huwa balke aap zabani tor par un sey baiat letey they. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurton sey sirf wohi ehad liya jis ka Allah ney hukm diya tha. aap ki hatheli kabhi kisi (ghair mehram) aurat ki hatheli sey nahin chhee. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aurton sey ehad letey to unhein zaban sey farmatey : mainey tum sey baiat ley li."
2876,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney do ghodon (ki daud) mein ghoda shamil kiya aur us ko yaqin nahin ke wo aagey badh jaeyga to ye (amal) juaa nahin. aur jisney do ghodon mein ghoda shamil kiya aur usey yaqin hai ke wo aagey badh jaeyga to ye juaa hai."
2877,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghodon ki tazmeer (mashaqqat ki trainig) ki. aap tazmeer shuda (mashaqqat ki trainig shuda) ghodon ko hafiya sey saniyatil-wadaa tak daudaatey they. aur ghair tazmeer shuda (mashaqqat ke ghair trainig shuda) ghodon ko Saniyatil-wadaa sey masjid bani Zuraiq tak."
2878,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daud sirf oont ghodey ki hoti hai."
2879,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dushman key ilaqey mein Quran ley kar safar karney sey mana farmaya, is khatrey sey ke wo dushman key haath mein aa jaeyga."
2880,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kiya ke aap dushman key ilaqey mein Quran ley kar safar karney sey mana farmatey they, is khatrey sey ke wo dushman key haath aa jaeyga."
2881,Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar khaibar key khums mein sey banu Haashim aur banu Muttlib ko milney waley hissey key barey mein baat cheet karney lagey. un dono ney kaha : aap ney hamarey bhaiyon (yani) banu Haashim aur banu Matlab ko hissa ata farmaya (aur hum bano Abd Shams ko nahin diya) halanke hamari qurbat eik hi (darjey ki) hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main banu Haashim aur banu Muttlib ko eik hi chiz samajhta hun.
